Example .env file:

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url_here
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_DEFAULT_KEY=your_supabase_publishable_key_here
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_browser_api_key_here
VITE_STM_PROXY_URL=http://localhost:8090
GOOGLE_MAPS_SERVER_API_KEY=your_google_maps_server_api_key_here

# Optional only if you have your own compare backend
# STM_COMPARE_UPSTREAM_URL=https://your-backend/transit/compare
# STM_COMPARE_UPSTREAM_API_KEY=your_backend_api_key
